# PROJECT RULES - READ BEFORE ANY ACTION

## Server & Domain
- This server: Adonis-farsi (SSH: Adonis-farsi)
- Persian site domain: adoniss.eu
- Project path: /root/adonis_site/
- Admin panel: https://adoniss.eu/admin/
- Restart: cd /root/adonis_site && bash restart.sh

## What NOT to do
- NEVER use /var/www/adonis_site/ — wrong server
- NEVER touch ubuntu-adonis server
- NEVER redirect adoniss.eu to adonisgroup.gr
- adonisgroup.gr = English site on a DIFFERENT server

## Django
- Persian frontend: /fa-new/ routes
- Gunicorn: 127.0.0.1:8000
- collectstatic required after every CSS change
